('143d1ea5-4404-4447-9735-4026b5eff9b4', 'Transparent Labs BULK: The Gold Standard Pre-Workout', 'Every ingredient clinically dosed, no proprietary blends, and no artificial sweeteners. BULK is what every pre-workout should aspire to be.', 'Citrulline Malate at a massive 8g for blood flow and pumps. Beta-Alanine 4g for endurance. Betaine 2.5g for power output. Caffeine 200mg with Theanine 200mg for smooth energy.', ARRAY['Fully transparent label', 'Clinical doses of everything', 'No artificial sweeteners', 'Smooth energy without crash'], 'Mix 1 scoop with 12 oz water 20-30 minutes before training.', ARRAY['200mg caffeine may be mild for stim-seekers', 'Premium price', 'Only available online'], 'Clean pre-workout enthusiasts who demand clinical dosing and transparent labeling.', 'Pre-Kaged Elite for higher stimulants. Gorilla Mode for more aggressive dosing. C4 for budget option.', 'Q: Is 200mg caffeine enough? A: For most people yes, especially paired with L-theanine for synergy. Stim veterans may want to add caffeine. Q: Why no artificial sweeteners? A: Transparent Labs uses stevia and natural flavors exclusively.', 9.2, '[{"name": "Tyler B.", "rating": 5, "text": "The cleanest energy and best pumps I have ever had. No crash, no jitters, just performance.", "verified": true, "date": "2026-01-14"}, {"name": "Alyssa R.", "rating": 5, "text": "Finally a pre-workout I can trust completely. Every ingredient dosed properly.", "verified": true, "date": "2025-12-28"}]'::jsonb),

